822
01:45:46,965 --> 01:45:51,525
Kakav bi to izazov bio!

823
01:46:07,845 --> 01:46:11,845
Zdravo, Tapi.

824
01:46:25,965 --> 01:46:28,645
Moja knjiga!

825
01:46:28,805 --> 01:46:32,325
Neko će mi objaviti knjigu!
Hana!

826
01:46:32,485 --> 01:46:36,965
