845
01:48:25,365 --> 01:48:28,765
Ne smeta im mnogo akcenat.

846
01:48:31,165 --> 01:48:35,445
Ne smeta ni meni.

847
01:48:35,605 --> 01:48:38,325
Tetka mi je ostavila Plamfild.

848
01:48:38,485 --> 01:48:43,365
